    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a sophisticated double-VANOS steplessly variable valve timing system, producing 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels through an M-Variable Differential Lock. This example has been meticulously maintained, with critical preventative service recently completed, including rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators. The chassis retains its structural rigidity, and the suspension maintains factory-spec damping and rebound characteristics. While the exterior shows light signs of use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil analysis and compression across all cylinders\u2014are excellent, ensuring the performance envelope remains fully accessible.",
      "price": 36500.0,
