    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish with only the slightest evidence of road wear, complemented by well-preserved alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and odor-free, with all leather surfaces, buttons, and technology features functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts effortlessly, backed by a consistent maintenance history that ensures peace of mind for the next owner. It is a reliable, well-sorted car that drives beautifully and looks sharp on the road.",
      "price": 33500.0,
