      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies consistent maintenance and mechanical integrity. This selection has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, this automobile offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite you to experience the superior handling and enduring value of this well-preserved specimen.",
      "price": 36800.0,
